Detailed Description

cvmx_agl_gmx_drv_ctl

AGL_GMX_DRV_CTL = GMX Drive Control

Notes: NCTL, PCTL, BYP_EN will be reset when MIX0_CTL[RESET] is set to 1. NCTL1, PCTL1, BYP_EN1 will be reset when MIX1_CTL[RESET] is set to 1.
